logical units (Constructs)
  - infrastructure code 
  - runtime code
  - configuration code



Stack for deployment model
- App repos (Asset tracking for Driver app)
  - Asset tracking for Driver app => repo 
      - Constructs definning the scopes and 
      - Stacks for groups of 
        - stateful resource 
        - stateless resource
  - DivineEvent Sourcing for Partner app => repo
    - Constructs definning the scopes and 
      - Stacks for groups of 
        - stateful resource 
        - stateless resource

  - Routing app handles routing the deliveries from Partners to Fleet's Driver.
    - Constructs definning the scopes and 
      - Stacks for groups of 
        - stateful resource 
        - stateless resource

